milestones.description: Tennekoon has become the top scorer for SL in ODIs with 137 runs, going past Tissera's 78
Tennekoon's 59 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for SL), surpassing Wettimuny's 53
de Silva has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for SL, going past Fernando
Glenn Turner and Geoff Howarth's 126-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 90 between Glenn Turner and Geoff Howarth
Tennekoon and Duleep Mendis's 30-run partnership is SL's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 22 between Tissera and Ranasinghe
Tony Opatha and de Silva's 24-run partnership is SL's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 22 between de Silva and Kaluperuma
